  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 9,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "ABOUT WINDMILLS"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 10,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "The Philippine Camping Ground\nClose Enough. Far Enough."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 12,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Windmills Camp Grounds is the go-to camping destination for the modern Filipino adventurer — close enough to Metro Manila, yet worlds away the moment you arrive. Perfect for barkada getaways, family reunion weekends, and corporate office outings. We provide the grounds, the scenery, and the facilities. You bring the tent, the crew, and the good vibes. Two locations, two experiences — both unforgettable."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 16,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Our Two Locations"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 19,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Tanay, Rizal — The Highland Camp"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 20,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Set in the cool emerald highlands of Tanay, Rizal — dramatic mountain terrain, misty mornings, cascading waterfalls, and sweeping Sierra Madre views. Just 2 hours from Manila."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 21,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "By Car: Via Marcos Highway (Marikina–Infanta Hwy) — approx. 1.5–2 hours depending on traffic."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 22,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Public Transport: Bus to Cubao, then jeepney or UV Express to Tanay — approx. 2–2.5 hrs from Cubao."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 23,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Address: Brgy. Cayabu, Tanay, Rizal 1980, Philippines"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 24,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Contact: +63 910 987 5807  ·  tanay@windmillscamp.ph"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 27,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Amadeo, Cavite — The Coffee Country Camp"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 28,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Perched in the rolling coffee-farm hills of Amadeo — the Philippines' barako capital. Crisp highland air, Taal views, and easy access from CAVITEX."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 29,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "By Car: Via CAVITEX or SLEX–Sta. Rosa exit — approx. 1.5 hours from Makati."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 30,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Public Transport: Bus to Tagaytay, then jeepney or van for hire toward Amadeo — approx. 20 mins from Tagaytay."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 31,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Address: Brgy. Dagatan, Amadeo, Cavite 4119, Philippines"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 32,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Contact: +63 910 987 5807  ·  amadeo@windmillscamp.ph"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 34,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "CAMPSITE AREAS"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 35,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Pick Your Spot, Pitch Your Tent"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 37,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Windmills Camp Grounds is a Bring Your Own Tent (BYOT) camping ground. Campers pitch their own tents at their reserved site. We provide the ground, facilities, and fire areas — you bring your tent, sleeping gear, and everything else you need for the perfect camp-out."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 38,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "BYOT Campsites — Tanay, Rizal"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 40,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "BYOT Campsites — Amadeo, Cavite"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 42,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Premium Private Tent Stays — Tanay, Rizal"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 43,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "These options include a fully set-up tent. No need to bring your own gear."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 45,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "* All rates are per person per night for BYOT sites, or per tent per night for premium stays."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 51,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "ACTIVITIES & EXPERIENCES"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 52,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "What to Do at Camp"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 54,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Tanay, Rizal — Experiences"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 55,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🏔 Mt. Daraitan Hike Summit views over Sierra Madre & Laguna de Bay"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 56,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "💦 Tinapak River & Falls Crystal clear river & limestone rock pools"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 57,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🔥 Barkada Firepit Kwentuhan, marshmallows & mountain air all night"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 58,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🌌 Stargazing Nights Zero light pollution — pure Milky Way views all night"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 59,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🧘 Mountain Yoga Sunrise sessions with sierra views"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 60,
