    "text": "🚣 Lake Kayaking Paddle Laguna de Bay at golden hour"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 61,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🍳 Camp Cooking Cook your own meals over firewood"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 62,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🐕 Dog Runs Open trails for your furry adventure buddy"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 63,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🚵 Mountain Biking Scenic highland trails for all levels"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 68,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Amadeo, Cavite — Experiences"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 69,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "☕ Coffee Farm Walk & Brew From bean to barako cup — guided tours"
