  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 75,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "🍳 Camp Cooking Cook your own meals over the fire"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 77,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "ON-SITE FACILITIES"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 78,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "We've Got the Grounds Covered"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 80,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Both camps provide clean, well-maintained facilities so you can focus on what matters — enjoying the outdoors. You bring your gear; we'll take care of the rest."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 81,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🚿 Clean Comfort Rooms"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 82,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Well-maintained CR and shower facilities with hot water — available to all campers throughout your stay."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 83,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🔥 Firepits & Firewood"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 84,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Every campsite comes with a dedicated firepit. Firewood is provided — just bring your lighter and camp recipes."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 85,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🚗 Parking Area"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 86,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Secured, on-site parking available for all registered campers. Each site comes with at least one parking slot."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 87,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "💡 Ground Lighting"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 88,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Ambient pathway lighting throughout the grounds for safe navigation after dark without ruining your night sky view."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 89,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🛒 Camp Store"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 90,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Forgot something? Our on-site store carries basic camping supplies, snacks, instant noodles, drinks, and firewood top-ups."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 91,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "☕ Coffee & Snack Bar"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 92,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Fresh brewed barako and local snacks available every morning. Amadeo camp serves beans straight from the farm."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 93,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🗑️ Waste Management"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 94,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Segregated waste bins across all grounds. We follow Leave No Trace principles — campers are expected to do the same."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 95,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "🏥 First Aid Station"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 96,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Basic first aid kit available at the camp office. Emergency contact numbers posted at all entry points."
  },
  {
