  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 142,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "RESERVATIONS"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 143,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "How to Book Your Campsite"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 145,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Book directly with us — no booking fees, no intermediaries. Flexible cancellation up to 48 hours before arrival. Perfect for barkada trips, office outings, and family reunions."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 146,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Reservation Process"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 147,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Step 1 — Choose Your Site"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 148,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Browse the campsite options above and pick your preferred site, dates, and number of campers."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 149,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Step 2 — Send a Reservation Request"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 150,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Contact us via phone, email, or Facebook Messenger with your: Full Name, Email, Phone Number, Camp Location, Campsite Type, Check-in & Check-out Dates, Number of Campers."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 151,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Step 3 — Pay the Downpayment"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 152,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Send 50% of the total rate as a downpayment via GCash to confirm your slot. Full balance is due upon arrival."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 153,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Step 4 — Send Payment Confirmation"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 154,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Screenshot your GCash receipt and send it to us via Messenger or email. We'll confirm your booking within 24 hours."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 155,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Step 5 — You're All Set!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 156,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "We'll send you a confirmation with directions, camp rules, and everything you need for your trip."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 157,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Payment via GCash"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 159,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "50% downpayment required to confirm reservation"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 160,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Remaining 50% balance is due upon arrival"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 161,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Use reference format: WIND-[YourName]-[CheckInDate]"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 162,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Send receipt screenshot to Messenger or email after payment"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 163,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Cancellation Policy"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 164,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Free cancellation up to 48 hours before arrival — full refund of downpayment"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 165,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Cancellation within 48 hours — downpayment is non-refundable"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 166,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "No-shows are non-refundable"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 167,
    "style": "List Bullet",
    "text": "Rescheduling is allowed with at least 24 hours' notice, subject to availability"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 169,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "CAMPER STORIES"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 170,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "Memories Made at Camp"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 172,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "\"Grabe, first time ko mag-camp and sobrang sulit! Our barkada went to the Starfield Site in Tanay — never seen so many stars in my life. Woke up to full Sierra Madre views at sunrise. 10/10, we're definitely coming back next month!\""
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 173,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "— Marco Santos, Makati, Metro Manila  |  Tanay Camp — Starfield Site"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 174,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "\"Brought our barkada to the Coffee Grove Site in Amadeo — woke up to the smell of fresh barako and morning mist. Super clean grounds, the staff were so nice, and the views were gorgeous! Total chillax vibes!\""
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 175,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "— Pia Reyes, BGC, Taguig  |  Amadeo Camp — Coffee Grove Site"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 176,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "\"We used the Meadow Group Site for our office outing — all 30 of us had a blast! From the interns to the bosses, everyone had fun. Tons of space, a big firepit, and the team bonding was sobrang saya.\""
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 177,
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "— Kuya Jun dela Cruz, Ortigas, Pasig  |  Amadeo Camp — Meadow Group Site"
  },
  {
